lead_paragraph: After five Big Ten players were ejected from games the first week of the season, conference coordinator of officials Bill Carollo has been spending an inordinate amount of time dissecting targeting penalties.

headline.print_headline: Head of Big Ten Officials: Week 1 Targeting Calls on Target
